  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Machinery Mechanics",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p><br />1) Perform maintenance, servicing and general repair of Forklift(electric forklifts and diesel forklifts), Trucks, CNC Machine and heavy machinery.<br />2) Able to troubleshooting and rectify Forklift, Trucks CNC Machine faults & defects.<br />3) Able to work independently with minimal supervision.<br />4) Maintain high standards in housekeeping and comply with all safety rules and regulations.<br />5) Minimum of 10 years relevant experiences.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><strong>Hands-on experience in troubleshooting, repairing, and maintaining heavy machinery, diesel engines, and hydraulic systems</strong>.</p><p><strong>Strong electrical knowledge</strong> with the ability to read and interpret electrical diagrams.</p><p>Solid understanding of AC & DC motors, single-phase and three-phase systems, lead-acid and lithium battery technologies, and electrical control circuits.</p><p>Prior experience in customer support will be an added advantage.<br /></p><p>Working hours: Monday - Fri （9:30am - 6pm) & Sat (9:30am - 5pm)</p><p><br />Send your resume to <strong>shundahardware@gmail.com</strong></p><p>Only shortlisted candidate would be notified</p>",
